{{Youmay|the [[Lightsaber crystal/Legends|lightsaber crystal]]|[[Sigil (disambiguation)|other uses of the name]]}}
[[File:Sigil-iw_sbrcrstl_006-KOTOR.png|right]]
Mined in the [[Sigil system/Legends|Sigil system]], the '''Sigil crystal''' was costly but worthwhile due to the searing effect it had once properly placed in a [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]]. It was a brownish-yellow color in nature, and when used in a [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]], the beam produced was incredibly potent and dealt greater damage. The [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Nemo]] had such a crystal; also the [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord]] [[Marka Ragnos]] had one in his possession.

